Amazing as always! It is like my home away from home... highly recommended!
My only go to place in this city. Raj is an amazing host with a doubt!
Located in the heart of the city, this cozy flat is spacious and well maintained. The host was super helpful and responsive, making our stay even better.
Comfortable stay. Smooth check-in processs. No disturbance. Great location, lot of eateries near the place. Last but not the least, the hosts were friendly and very responsive. Highly recommend!
Plenty of space; in a good walkable area. Building was under construction, but no loud noises noted at night. Clean.

The listing location is correct and the hosts were very friendly and helpful to guide us through the checkin process. The listing is beautiful but very dirty the time I checked in, therefore I had to checkout the same time/cancel the reservation.
A very neat and clean apartment. Rajni is a wonderful person as he was very compassionate with his words and responsive.

The host is absolutely amazing …a warm friendly person ever ready to help out whenever he’s called …location is excellent and being a new apartment is in top condition ….would highly recommend this to fellow travellers looking for a good comfortable stay at a reasonable budget in the heart of Siliguri

This place is at great location, flat is good and Raj will look after for anything u need during the stay.
I recommend everyone this place to have a smooth check in and pleasant stay.

Such a pleasant stay. Can't expect more. People who want a place near the market, this is the best. The place was very clean, well equipped with essentials, shops around where we can get almost everything. The host Raj and Rajni were very friendly, kind and helpful. This place will be my first choice whenever am going to visit Siliguri next time. I would recommend the same to everybody.
Awesome stay... awesome hosts.. keep up the good work!

With easy access to the main road, eateries, medicine shops etc, my stay at the apartment was a comfortable one. Both the owner and the caretaker were very helpful and the caretaker was just a phone call away. Would visit again when in Siliguri.
The host, Raj, was extremely hospitable, accommodating and helpful. The property manager Sumana is an angel! Will definitely re-visit. Highly recommended!
